text: Assiya İpek (born December 5, 1993) is a Turkish woman weightlifter competing in the 69 kg division. İpek earned a quota spot for the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1993 births Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Turkish female weightlifters Category:Weightlifters at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic weightlifters of Turkey
